race.description: Parma Pot Luck Deal At Wbl Greys (300+)
race.comment: GRAY ELLIOT (8) produced an impressive win last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by 4.5 lengths (25.45) at Ballarat. Hard to go past. BUSH LASS (1) was below best at her last start when 7th at Geelong following a second place finish (25.54) at this track two back. Has a good record here at this journey. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. LEKTRA HOPPER (2) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing eighth (30.74) last time in a Grade 6 at Mt Gambier. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Worth another chance. BOB DEEDS (7) can feature with the right run.
